<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>لوَكِيله خَالعهَا بِمِائَة لم ينقص<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span>وَكيله<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
